As an Admin, I'd like authorization to create, update, and delete services.

As an Admin, I'd like authorization to delete inappropriate user reviews.

As a User, I'd like to to sign up for a personal account & maintain my account (update/delete) via a profile page.

As a User, I'd like authorization to leave reviews on specific services.

As a User, I'd like to visit the site via a landing page with basic info about services offered, including navigation options for perusing the site. Nav options should include links to visit 'Home', 'Shop', & 'My Account'. 

As a User, I'd like to see a list of all services offered.

As a User, I'd like to see a detail page for each specific service, including an area for my review of that service.
